    <stitle>13 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-14613 - INSTALL - GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check the shifter housing assembly to make sure shift block and yoke notches are aligned in
                the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13027s6">Figure 286</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13027s6" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027s6" filename="../figg13/G13027s6.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 286. Make Sure Shift Block and Yoke Notches are Aligned in Neutral Position</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Loctite 242 to the bolt threads. Install the retaining bolts and tighten to 35 to 45
                ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#183; m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13027s7">Figure 287</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13027s7" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027s7" filename="../figg13/G13027s7.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 287. Install Retaining Bolts and Tighten</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
